 thought: I've confirmed that both datasets use the same ID format (rec + alphanumeric). The attendance table has 326 rows and the events table has 42 rows. Now I need to perform the join, group by event, count attendees, filter for >10 attendees, then filter for type='Meeting' and count the final results.
 action: execute_python
 action_input: {'code': 'import pandas as pd\nimport sqlite3\n\n# Read attendance CSV\nattendance_df = pd.read_csv(\'csv/attendance.csv\')\n\n# Connect to SQLite database and read events table\nconn = sqlite3.connect(\'db/event.db\')\nevents_df = pd.read_sql_query("SELECT * FROM event", conn)\nconn.close()\n\n# Step 1: Join attendance with events on link_to_event = event_id\nmerged_df = pd.merge(attendance_df, events_df, left_on=\'link_to_event\', right_on=\'event_id\', how=\'inner\')\nprint(f"After merge: {len(merged_df)} records")\n\n# Step 2: Group by event and count attendees per event\nattendees_per_event = merged_df.groupby([\'event_id\', \'event_name\', \'type\']).size().reset_index(name=\'attendee_count\')\nprint(f"\\nAttendees per event:")\nprint(attendees_per_event.head(10))\n\n# Step 3: Filter for >10 attendees\nfiltered_events = attendees_per_event[attendees_per_event[\'attendee_count\'] > 10]\nprint(f"\\nEvents with >10 attendees: {len(filtered_events)}")\nprint(filtered_events)\n\n# Step 4: Filter for type=\'Meeting\'\nmeeting_events = filtered_events[filtered_events[\'type\'] == \'Meeting\']\nprint(f"\\nMeeting events with >10 attendees: {len(meeting_events)}")\nprint(meeting_events)\n\n# Final result\nfinal_result = {\n    \'total_attendance_records\': len(attendance_df),\n    \'total_events\': len(events_df),\n    \'events_with_attendance\': len(merged_df[\'event_id\'].unique()),\n    \'events_with_more_than_10_attendees\': len(filtered_events),\n    \'meeting_events_with_more_than_10_attendees\': len(meeting_events),\n    \'meeting_details\': meeting_events.to_dict(\'records\') if len(meeting_events) > 0 else []\n}\n\nprint(f"\\n=== FINAL RESULTS ===")\nprint(f"Total attendance records: {final_result[\'total_attendance_records\']}")\nprint(f"Total events: {final_result[\'total_events\']}")\nprint(f"Events with attendance: {final_result[\'events_with_attendance\']}")\nprint(f"Events with >10 attendees: {final_result[\'events_with_more_than_10_attendees\']}")\nprint(f"Meeting events with >10 attendees: {final_result[\'meeting_events_with_more_than_10_attendees\']}")'} 
